          "snippet": "\"Honestly the rudest staff at the pharmacy check out.\"",
          "thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-GkcfnY9VuEfi4RaD9h8N7OWX-yuQetZdda3IWnDd9kf7TA=s40-k-cc-rp-mo"
        },
        {
          "snippet": "\"Terrible service and I\u2019d go somewhere else but this location is convenient\"",
          "thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVysApXWH3A46hPf-kCpJ6KsTYfIiGnepYbG_1BLgNWsYB37l7k=s40-k-cc-rp-mo"
