      "most_relevant": [
        {
          "username": "she who shall not be named",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "110069458656433624971",
          "user_review_count": 3,
          "user_photo_count": 1,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDlMdNzJ20laa8V0EgTPLB2GQtAnEYRMdEv-HgUAbvdTGEhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I never write reviews especially negative ones unless absolutely warranted. This Duane Reade doesn't necessarily have the most shining reviews so my one star is being added into the ether - but this complaint is directed towards one employee and one employee only. I live in the neighborhood and I regularly make pickup orders on the walgreens app to limit my in person interaction at this location as little as possible. For some reason every time I come into pickup, Saha who is at the register acts like it is his literal first day on earth. Every single time. He is so consistent in his miserable, helpless, and pathetic attitude its actually kind of impressive. It takes two seconds to ask for my name and to grab my order. I am not in the business of stealing someone else's toilet paper or mascara. Yet it is easier to sneak drugs through Russian airport security or compete and win an Olympic gold medal than for Saha to look at my name on the walgreens app and grab my items. He has me repeat my name multiple times, show him my confirmation message,  point out my name on said message and sometimes even show identification. I understand taking precaution but he is so painfully inefficient, slow and dumb it makes me wonder if he just likes to waste people's time. And to top it all off he still sneers at me with total skepticism regarding my identity once shoving my order into my hands. Everyone else at this location is an absolute gem and doesn't look at me with complete dumbfoundedness when I tell them I'm picking up an order. Except for Saha. I dread when I see him at the counter. Sometimes I try even cutting the line to avoid speaking to him and his lack of helpfulness altogether because our unecessarily extended encounters send me into rage every time. Please for the love of god fire this man. Thank you.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCNFZIQmZNbEZOVHpjM01XMTVkbVY2TW5Bd01rRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x8e9c134b253e524!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlB4VHBfMlFNTzc3MW15dmV6MnAwMkE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "4 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-02-20T00:51:46+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Philip Ujlaki",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "105926089308968807142",
          "user_review_count": 11,
          "user_photo_count": 1,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzkXBcOpD8fCN0kd9B5tbaAb0s5R93EIEn_2DvHr7LswrPs9Cx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "This is, without exaggeration, one of the worst pharmacies I have ever encountered. The staff are consistently incompetent, dismissive, and shockingly rude. You can be told your prescription is ready, arrive promptly, and then be flat-out refused because they feel like working on their own timeline. Every single visit is a guaranteed waste of time\u2014whether it\u2019s their inability to locate a basic prescription or the absurd discovery that they had my profile duplicated under two different names and never noticed. On my last two visits, I was given open attitude and condescension simply for stating that I was in a rush, as if urgency were an unreasonable request. If you\u2019ve ever seen how pharmacies operate in literally any other country, this place is an embarrassing failure and a complete travesty of what a pharmacy is supposed to be.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xjeFJGUm5XbTlZUkZZM1dHZFZRVEpZYVhKSmVXYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x8e9c134b253e524!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlcxRFRnWm9YRFY3WGdVQTJYaXJJeWc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "4 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-02-02T19:44:35+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Laura Desiree",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "110872938519938871394",
