          "description": "the meanest of the mean, ice cold crew behind the pharmacy counter. But once you learn the protocol of approaching when the desk is clear, stating simply your purpose (and I mean as simple as \"prescription pick up please\"), state your DOB and do not ask a single follow-up question, you are fine.",
