          "description": "I\u2019ve always been pleased with the service at this Duane Reade on Spring Street and Lafayette. The automated system lets me know when my prescription is ready. They\u2019re usually isn\u2019t a very big line. They also do vaccinations and other injections and it\u2019s easy to get an appointment. There are also good snacks and cosmetics, and there is an elevator to the basement where the pharmacy is.",
