          "description": "This is incorrect the pharmacy closes at 8.\nThe pharmacist are so rude I\u2019ve never experienced anything like it. There\u2019s one woman in particular who makes me feel like an unwelcome freak every time I go in. They are unorganized and lie when they are lazy. My doctor called in a prescription and had proof that the pharmacy received it but the pharmacy kept saying it was cancelled. I had my doctor call them and after 10 min of back and forth they said \u201cohhhh\u201d and magically found my prescription. Terrible service and I\u2019d go somewhere else but this location is convenient",
